<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Threads & Facebook 影片下載器</title>
  <style>
    body {
      width: 320px;
      padding: 16px;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    }

    .container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .status {
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .status.active {
      background: #dcfce7;
      color: #15803d;
    }

    .status.inactive {
      background: #fee2e2;
      color: #dc2626;
    }

    .instructions {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .instructions ol {
      margin: 8px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .instructions li {
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding-top: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #999;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>📥 Threads & Facebook 影片下載器</h1>

    <div id="status" class="status inactive">
      不在 Threads 或 Facebook 網站
    </div>

    <div class="instructions">
      <strong>使用方法：</strong>
      <ol>
        <li>前往 threads.net、threads.com 或 facebook.com</li>
        <li>找到貼文或留言中的影片</li>
        <li>點擊右上角的下載按鈕</li>
        <li>開始下載</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <a href="#" id="privacyLink">隱私權政策</a> | v1.1.0
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="popup.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
